## Backup Directory Discovery

The most interesting discovery was:

```text
/backup/
```

Inside the backup directory was an encrypted RSA private key.

```text
-----BEGIN RSA PRIVATE KEY-----
Proc-Type: 4,ENCRYPTED
...
-----END RSA PRIVATE KEY-----
```

This immediately looked promising.

My assumption was that the key could provide SSH access if I could recover the passphrase.

